l of Service (DoS/DDoS) attacks, social engineering, spamming, or phishing attacks against our employees or clients."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Provide us a reasonable amount of time to resolve the issue before disclosing it publicly."}],["$","li",null,{"children":["Submit your detailed findings, including steps to reproduce the vulnerability, to ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Support@ftfxtechsolutions.com"}],"."]}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"legal-module__8113wq__section","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"legal-module__8113wq__sectionTitle","children":"Our Response"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"legal-module__8113wq__text","children":"Upon receiving your report, our engineering team will acknowledge receipt within 48 hours. We will investigate the issue and provide an estimated timeline for a patch. We commit to not pursuing legal action against security researchers who comply with this Responsible Disclosure Policy and act in good faith."}]]}]]}]}],["$","$L3",null,{}]]}],[["$","link","0",{"rel":"stylesheet","href":"/_next/static/chunks/3izcsvynze-sw.css","precedence":"next"}],["$","script","script-0",{"src":"/_next/static/chunks/3dzb2wvsg6dxw.js","async":true}]],["$","$L4",null,{"children":["$","$5",null,{"name":"Next.MetadataOutlet","children":"$@6"}]}]]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"buildId":"6JxBV_Py11TqinohXGaBP"}
